Citations
Date: 0/0/1949
Source: High Country Days
Author: NEWTON
Vol / Page: 159
Edition:
Quote: Brownie was to do the top and the head shepherd would be 'under the top' - his beat would be through the basins where the snow lay deep and the going would be the heaviest.
